ations behind attacks and their societal impact [95] Dual role of AI in cybersecurity and legal frameworks Omits motivations and societal aspects [88] AI-enabled social engineering attacks Lacks exploration of motivations behind attacks countermeasures, and it serves as a resource for those interested in developing solutions to thwart increasingly sophisticated ML-powered attacks in IoT environments.",
